MobileRecallProductLot is a Form
    title is "LotNumber"
    Layout
        single column
            RecallNotice
                display as text
            RecallNotice.Name
                display as text
            RecallProduct.ProductName
                display only
            visible when (RecallProductLot not entered)
                RecallProductLot
            visible when (SingleLot)
                RecallProductLot
                    display as text
            visible when (HasRange)
                two column table
                    column1
                        RecallProductLot
                            label is "LotRange"
                            display as text
                    column2
                        ThruLot
                            label is "Thru"
                            display as text
            ExpirationDate
